    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="CH1a0903-start">
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_001-1a.1-h" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T16:04:48.729+09:00">The Foundation of the Way</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-29T18:09:28.086+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-29T18:09:37.377+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-29T18:09:30.421+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-29T18:09:32.628+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:33:08.209+09:00">Beautiful material becomes regarded as precious by being circulated;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:44:20.296+09:00">Great talent becomes recognised as having ability by being noticed.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T16:29:28.753+09:00">What can I use to explain this?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:45:45.866+09:00">The Piannan tree and the camphor tree are the most renowned of trees in the world.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T16:46:50.783+09:00">They grow in the midst of deep mountains</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T16:47:06.063+09:00">and by the banks of streams.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:36:51.499+09:00">When they stand tall, they count as the venerable ancestors of all trees;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:36:59.413+09:00">when felled, they serve as material for myriad generations.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T16:51:30.435+09:00">Floating on the streams of mountain rivers,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T16:52:39.398+09:00">they emerge on dusky plains.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T18:10:27.096+09:00">where they follow the course of the Blue and Yellow Rivers,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T18:10:30.002+09:00">to reach the imperial capital;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T18:10:41.012+09:00">through the efforts of carpenters,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T18:10:47.869+09:00">they here reveal their patterns and colors.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:15:54.879+09:00">being dense and elongated,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:14:13.414+09:00">Being stout and having straight grain,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:17:08.68+09:00">insects and wood-worms cannot bore into them</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:17:23.798+09:00">and water and dampness cannot harm them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:20:44.349+09:00">They are soft and flexible at the top,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:20:49.196+09:00">and hard and strong where they enter the ground.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:24:22.541+09:00">Their luster develops without being waxed or polished,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:22:56.807+09:00">their patterns form without being carved or painted.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:26:14.183+09:00">Above, they become treasures for emperors and kings;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:39:11.085+09:00">below, they are awarded to high officials,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:39:21.735+09:00">while commoners are not allowed to use them for tools or implements.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:31:02.76+09:00">If they are blocked at passes and fords,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:31:48.131+09:00">or hindered by barriers of mountain slopes,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T17:32:58.869+09:00">or separated by the embankments of the Nine Pools;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T23:33:35.126+09:00">Those who wish to enrich the country and reinforce their authority,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.1-h" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T23:33:01.399+09:00">Supreme Virtue</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T23:34:20.498+09:00">open up new territory and subjugate far-off states</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T23:43:01.644+09:00">must achieve this through their people.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T23:35:16.971+09:00">Those who want to establish merit and enhance their reputation,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T23:37:27.7+09:00">spread their fame and manifest their glory</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T00:20:45.303+09:00">must obtain this through their own person.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T23:37:46.744+09:00">Hence, if there is one who possesses a state of ten thousand chariots,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T00:25:53.659+09:00">controls the life and death of the people,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T00:25:30.699+09:00">monopolizes the bounty of the mountains and marshes,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:13:26.865+09:00">and commands a host of soldiers,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T00:21:08.141+09:00">but who does not have any merit in his person</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-20T23:40:30.302+09:00"> and whose name is not manifested in the world,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T00:21:31.071+09:00"> this must be due to faults in the principles of his rule.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:31:03.138+09:00"/>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:31:00.051+09:00">the multitudes will rally around someone who harbors virtue</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:31:04.651+09:00">According to the nature of Heaven and Earth</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:31:01.504+09:00">and the various classes of the Myriad Things</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:30:49.274+09:00">whereas they will fear someone who relies on punishments.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:30:43.867+09:00">If they rally around him, they will amass by his side;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:30:41.003+09:00">if they fear him, then they will leave his environs.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:30:30.971+09:00">Hence, one who sets up punishments should not avoid making them too light;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:30:29.394+09:00">one who practices virtue should not avoid increasing it;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:30:21.118+09:00">one who carries out punishments should not worry that they are too slight;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:30:14.696+09:00">one who distributes rewards should not worry that they are too generous.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-2a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:32:37.537+09:00">By these means, he will become close with those who are near to him and attract those who are distant.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:34:45.664+09:00">If punishments are heavy, you will have a troubled heart;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:43:33.129+09:00">if your duties are  many, your body will be exhausted</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:42:38.839+09:00">If your heart is troubled, punishments will be haphazard and will not be established;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:43:40.87+09:00">if your body is exhausted, then all things will go awry and nothing will succeed.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:44:04.854+09:00">Therefore, when a noble man governs,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:44:47.76+09:00">he is serene, as though he has no duties</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:58:00.056+09:00">and tranquil, as though there is no sound.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:59:56.573+09:00">It is as if there are no clerks in the government offices,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T16:46:47.074+09:00">and no people in the towns,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:01:43.884+09:00">There are no disputes in the alleyways of the villages,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:03:49.919+09:00">and the old and young do not complain in the courtyards.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:05:09.296+09:00">Those that are close to have nothing to criticize;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:05:23.626+09:00">those that are distant from him have nothing to make known to him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:07:07.576+09:00">the postal stations have no clerks traveling at night;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:07:38.713+09:00">in the villages there are no impositions announced at night.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:07:50.785+09:00">Dogs do not bark at night;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:11:31.205+09:00">cocks do not cry at night.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:12:04.645+09:00">The elderly enjoy their food in their halls;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:12:11.292+09:00">and the able-bodied males plow in their fields.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:12:40.071+09:00">Those who are at court are loyal to their ruler,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:12:54.811+09:00">those who are at home are filial toward their parents.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:30:29.984+09:00">If  one now embellishes [the people] by rewarding the good and punishing the wicked</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:30:35.708+09:00">and educates them by establishing national and local schools,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:32:30.99+09:00">then the worthy and the foolish will have different appraisals,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:33:10.6+09:00">and the scrupulous and despicable will be given different gradings,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:35:01.761+09:00">seniors and juniors [abide by] different rules of propriety,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:37:55.455+09:00">and superiors and inferiors be ranked,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:36:04.388+09:00">the strong and the weak will support one another,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:50:14.054+09:00">and the honored and the base will serve one another,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:37:29.155+09:00">those of younger and older age will care for one another,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:50:17.966+09:00">following one another like geese flying in formation.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:48:42.358+09:00">Though he does not speak, he is trusted;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:49:05.742+09:00">though he is not angered, he inspires awe.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_008-3a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T17:47:46.995+09:00">Does one really have to have strong armor and sharp weapons, deep dungeons and harsh regulations, instructions repeated morning and evening, before one can carry this out?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:09:07.474+09:00">they might topple from lofty mountains</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:40:03.628+09:00">or fall into distant and dark creeks;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:40:40.681+09:00">where trees are lush, spreading so as to leave no space,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:21:16.786+09:00">or rocks are lofty and craggy so as to be impassable;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:18:13.805+09:00">where it is so broad that no boats or carts can reach them</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:41:08.13+09:00">or it is so narrow that there is no path where one can walk with a shoulder pole;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:21:23.608+09:00">where merchants do not reach</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:41:19.085+09:00">and artisans do not spy;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.38" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:21:36.874+09:00">where those who know them do not see them</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:41:30.251+09:00">and those who see them do not know them.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:22:19.169+09:00">Their merit is discarded and their virtue perishes,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:23:11.518+09:00">they rot and dry out,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:23:31.208+09:00">and roll down gullies a hundred fathoms deep,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:24:47.503+09:00">frightened and stiff.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:25:59.287+09:00">At this time,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:42:05.17+09:00">they are worth less than a withered poplar by the roadside,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:29:50.335+09:00">piled up and twisted,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:30:46.038+09:00">bent and uneven.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:31:43.697+09:00">But if they grow in spacious areas by a great city,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:32:48.407+09:00">near famed master artisans,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:35:14.22+09:00">then their timber will be hewn,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:42:22.674+09:00">and measured with a compass and T-square,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:42:43.594+09:00">then the solid will patch whatever is rotten,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:36:39.734+09:00">and whatever is too short will be lengthened.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.54" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:37:26.631+09:00">From the larger pieces zun-goblets are fashioned,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.55" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T22:37:49.769+09:00">and from the smaller ones shang-goblets,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.56" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:43:03.126+09:00">decorated with cinnabar lacquer</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.57" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T23:09:04.527+09:00">and chiseled to become bright.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.58" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T23:09:48.15+09:00">The ruler prepares the tailao sacrifice;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T00:55:07.826+09:00">and performs rituals at the local schools in spring and autumn;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.60" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T23:42:16.015+09:00">he dresses in patterned silks,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.61" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:44:00.88+09:00">and attends the ceremony with gravity and dignity;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.62" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T00:55:36.033+09:00">he wears his headgear and belt with the proper countenance,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.63" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:44:24.838+09:00">and faces the wine and fills a round of cups.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.64" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T23:23:30.947+09:00">Ministers stand arrayed,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.65" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T23:25:51.743+09:00">paraded in the palace halls.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.66" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T00:56:12.584+09:00">Those who gaze from afar become dazed in their eyes,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.67" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T00:56:22.744+09:00">while those who are near smell the fragrance in their noses.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.68" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T23:38:50.204+09:00">Hence, if things are obstructed, they will be cut off,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.69" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:45:07.639+09:00">but if they are put in their proper sequence, they will be noticed;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.70" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T23:43:14.288+09:00">if they are repressed, they will sink down,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.71" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T00:56:56.33+09:00">but if they are advanced, they will rise up.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.72" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T23:28:40.603+09:00">In their place of origin, Pian and catalpa trees</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.73" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-21T23:43:35.077+09:00">are worth less than a withered poplar,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.74" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:45:56.801+09:00">It is not the case that they are very different As regards  virtue and beauty,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.75" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:46:17.69+09:00"> or with regard to talent and strength,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.76" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:46:34.579+09:00">but while some will wither and be discarded in remote places,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.77" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-23T03:46:42.06+09:00">some will be used to make vessels for the ancestral temple:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.78" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T00:57:38.356+09:00">it is all a question of whether they are noticed or not –</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-1a.79" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T00:57:40.063+09:00">and with men it is the same.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:32:23.391+09:00">People living in remote marshes</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:32:37.969+09:00">and men who wield the plow,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:33:22.988+09:00">in some cases bear unfettered abilities in their breasts,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:34:18.684+09:00">and posses the admirable qualities that Yu and Gaoyao had.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:34:58.238+09:00">The guidelines lie within them</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:36:29.936+09:00">and the methods of a myriad generation are stored in their hearts,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:37:04.687+09:00">but they are not welcomed by this world</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:37:34.165+09:00"> because no one has introduced and made them noticed.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:38:11.754+09:00">The sons and younger brothers of senior ministers</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:37:52.329+09:00">as well as partisans and associates of noble families,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:38:33.258+09:00">even though they have noabilities that surpass those of others,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:39:00.406+09:00">are placed in esteemed and important positions:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:40:02.45+09:00">those who support them are strong, those who commend them are crafty,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-2a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:40:07.239+09:00">so there is nothing they cannot attain.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:41:39.564+09:00">In the past, there was Bian Que who lived in Song.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:42:32.127+09:00">He had offende the ruler of Song</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:42:35.351+09:00">and fled to Wei.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:42:47.208+09:00">In Wei there was a man who was about to die of an illness.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:43:00.509+09:00">Bian Que arrived at his home,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:40:54.366+09:00">The father of the sick man told Bian Que:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:43:07.476+09:00">wishing to cure him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:41:07.985+09:00">“My son is critically ill.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:43:33.176+09:00">We are about to welcome a better physician to cure him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:43:52.651+09:00">This is not something that you would be able to cure!”</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:45:44.453+09:00">He sent him off without employing him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:46:06.373+09:00">Thereupon he engaged a shaman to ask for good fortune and pray for his son’s life.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:44:30.255+09:00">[The shaman] faced Bian Que and made incantations,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:46:59.931+09:00">but the sick man died in the end:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:44:58.281+09:00">Bian Que was the best physician in the world,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:47:27.497+09:00">but could not compete with a shaman for employment:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:48:06.402+09:00">it is all a question of whether they are recognized or not.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:45:13.179+09:00">the shaman was unable to cure him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:52:28.023+09:00">Thus, when problems arise, to seek those who are far off while neglecting those who are close by,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:51:18.275+09:00">to hoard the broad while discarding the narrow:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-3a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T18:52:02.212+09:00">this is what this is called.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:51:21.124+09:00">In the past, there was Gong Zhi Qi who formulated strategies for the Lord of Yu.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:52:11.809+09:00">He wanted to decline Lord Xian of Jin’s bribes of jade disks and horses</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:52:40.564+09:00">and not grant him right of way along the  road to Xiayang.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:52:59.217+09:00">Was this not a plan worthy of being inscribed in bronze and stone?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:56:43.62+09:00">However, that the Lord of Yu did not listen</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-4a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:54:10.938+09:00">was because he was deluded by the exquisite and rare treasures.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-4a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:54:46.906+09:00">It was not the case that the virtuous conduct of Baoqiu</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-4a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:54:56.419+09:00"> was inferior to that of Li Si or Zhao Gao,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-4a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:57:04.916+09:00">but he lived secluded in a  thatched hut</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-4a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:57:16.858+09:00">and was not employed by the world –</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-4a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:57:47.002+09:00"> ministers with harsh tongues calumniated him.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:58:15.498+09:00">Everybody knows that good is good</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:59:15.581+09:00">everybody knows that learning has benefits to oneself</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-06-30T19:29:44.911+09:00">and that bad is bad;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T19:59:53.182+09:00">and that laziness and levity do not benefit one’s affairs.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-06-30T19:31:01.973+09:00">But those who act in this way have excessive desires</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:02:02.381+09:00">and are unable to overcome their yearning.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:02:28.753+09:00">All rulers know that they should seek out worthies to help them,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:02:45.947+09:00">to draw worthies near to assist them,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:03:09.828+09:00">yet worthies and sages sometimes live secluded in dwellings in the fields</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:03:19.303+09:00"> and do not take part in state affairs:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-06-30T19:34:21.887+09:00">this is because the officials who observe and listen are not cognizant about those below,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-06-30T19:34:48.609+09:00">causing criticism for blocking talent to be directed against the ruler.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:35:29.751+09:00">If criticism for blocking talent is directed against the ruler,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:08:45.652+09:00">then loyal and worthy men will be neglected in the wilderness;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:10:08.185+09:00">if  loyal and worthy men are neglected in the wilderness,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:10:10.676+09:00">then factions of sycophantic ministers will be present at court;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:10:13.898+09:00">if factions of sycophantic ministers are present at court,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:10:16.509+09:00">then inferiors will not be loyal to their ruler;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:10:23.767+09:00">if inferiors are not loyal to their ruler,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-06-30T19:40:42.306+09:00">then those above will not understand those below;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:11:03.291+09:00">if those above do not understand those below,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#CH1a0903_CHANT_007-5a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#oesterg" modified="2020-05-22T20:11:26.105+09:00">this is the reason why the empire will be toppled.</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
